  "title": "Azure Firewall",
  "contentHtml": "Michael Howard, Gladys Rodriguez and Mark Simos with guest Suren Jamiyanaa&nbsp;\n                     (\n                        <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/suren-jamiyanaa-a0515b10b/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                     ) \n                     who is a Program Manager (PM) in the Azure Firewall team.\n      \n                     <br>\n                     In this episode we cover recent security news including the latest on the SolarWinds attack and updates for Security Center, Azure Stream Analytics, Google's Web Signin, Power BI and BGP improvements.\n      \n                     <br><br>\n                     <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/115761?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"rss embed thingy\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/248603/\">TTTTTT | RSS.com Podcasting</a></iframe>\n      \n                     <h5>Links</h5> \n                     <ul>\n                        <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/115761/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-pencil\"></i></a></li>\n                        <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://aka.ms/solorigate'>Solorigate Resources</a></li>\n                        <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/security-center/continuous-export?tabs=azure-portal'>Continuously export Security Center data</a></li>\n                        <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/microsoft-security-and/security-community-webinars/ba-p/927888'>Security Community Webinars</a></li>\n                        <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/additional-support-for-managed-identity-in-azure-stream-analytics/'>Additional support for managed identity in Azure Stream Analytics now in public preview</a></li>\n                        <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/deprecation-of-webview-support-announcement-from-google/'>Deprecation of webview sign-in support announcement from Google</a></li>\n                        <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/blog/microsoft-introduces-steps-to-improve-internet-routing-security/'>Microsoft introduces steps to improve internet routing security</a></li>\n                        <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://powerbi.microsoft.com/en-us/blog/announcing-new-admin-apis-and-service-principal-authentication-to-make-for-better-tenant-metadata-scanning/'>Power BI: New Admin APIs and Service Principal authentication to make for better tenant metadata scanning</a></li>\n                        <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/firewall/overview'>What is Azure Firewall</a></li>\n                        <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/services/azure-firewall/'>Azure Firewall - Cloud-native network security to protect your Azure Virtual Network resources</a></li>\n                        <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_upMCevX5xQ&t=102s'>What is cloud-native Azure Network Security | Azure Network Security Part 1</a></li>\n                     </ul>"
